com.nutiteq.editable.layers

Class EditableGeometryLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nutiteq.layers.Layer
      • com.nutiteq.vectorlayers.VectorLayer<com.nutiteq.geometry.Geometry>
        • com.nutiteq.vectorlayers.GeometryLayer
          • com.nutiteq.editable.layers.EditableGeometryLayer

  • public class EditableGeometryLayer
extends com.nutiteq.vectorlayers.GeometryLayer
    Geometry layer with extra functions for editing elements. Supports all kind of geometries: Points, Lines and Polygons Can connect to any editable data source (data source that supports EditableVectorDataSource interface)
    Author:
    mtehver
